.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/172326/', '', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, Thalidomide, Belimumab, More', 'Pertuzumab, Rucaparib, Tisagenlecleucel, Aminolevulinic acid, Tazemetostat, Altretamine, Tagraxofusp, Sotorasib, Enasidenib, Belzutifan, Mitotane, More', 1767369485);
